      <scopecontent id="aspace_c55f341835f7cf59b7ef6c6ec91f8c79">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This record group documents Mutch's work as a prominent author of religious education curricular materials during the first half of this century.</p>
         <p>The Correspondence of Series I primarily relates to Mutch's <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>Graded Bible Studies,</part>
            </title> which were used extensively in the U. S. and translated into Chinese. Writings and Sermons in Series II include copies of his religious education textbooks as well as a sermon delivered at the 35th anniversary of the Howard Avenue Congregational Church in New Haven, and a memoir by Mutch. The Notes and Lectures of Series III include documention of Mutch's work as a professor at Ripon College.</p>
         <p>Some printed materials received with the Mutch Papers have been placed in other Yale Divinity Library record groups. The following materials related to the Howard Avenue Congregational Church in New Haven were placed in Record Group No. 48, New England Church Records:</p>    
         <list listtype="unordered">
            <item>Manual (annotated) - 1887</item>
            <item>Programs for "Service of Praise" - 1887, 1888</item>
            <item>List of officers and members - 1888</item>
            <item>Manual - 1891</item>
            <item>Yearbook - 1892</item>
            <item>Historical brochure - 1895</item>
            <item>Manual (annotated) - 1897</item>
            <item>Program for 35th anniversary program - 1900</item>
            <item>Church newsletter - 1901</item>
            <item>Sunday School lesson outline - n.d.</item>
         </list>
         <p>The following materials were placed in Record Group No. 56, Congregational Church Records:</p>    
         <list listtype="unordered">
            <item>
               <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Constitution and Rules of the Associated Pastors of New Haven Center</part>
               </title> - 1873</item>
            <item>
               <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>The Creed and Confession of Faith</part>
               </title> - 1884</item>
            <item>
               <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Manual of the New Haven Congregational Club</part>
               </title> - 1889</item>
            <item>
               <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Articles of Association and By-Laws of the Congregational Union of New Haven</part>
               </title> - 1892</item>
         </list>
      </scopecontent>
